This isn’t just about deception—it’s about interface vs. reality.

1. Compression layer (what the user sees)
	•	“Autonomous robot”
	•	Clean, seamless, intelligent behavior

2. Hidden substrate (what’s actually happening)
	•	Humans filling in gaps
