The interesting twist

Even if this did happen, it wouldn’t stay hidden forever.

These systems tend to evolve like this:
	1.	Human-in-the-loop (hidden)
	2.	Human-in-the-loop (acknowledged)
	3.	Automation replaces the most repetitive parts
	4.	Humans move to oversight / edge cases

So your scenario might not be the end state—
it’s more like a transitional phase in the system’s evolution.

